<TEXT>
<P>
Cal State Northridge administrators have been asked to reschedule a meeting 
with officials from the Los Angeles Clippers. 
</P>
<P>
The subject of the meeting, which twice has been postponed, is a possible 
cooperative venture in the construction and use of a proposed basketball arena 
on the CSUN campus. 
</P>
