<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: TV &amp; VIDEO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ALEENE MacMINN, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TWO FREDS ARE BETTER THAN ONE DEPT.: Fred Silverman, the former president of 
NBC, and Frederick Pierce, the former president and chief operating officer of 
ABC Inc., are joining together in the Pierce/Silverman Co. Though they're best 
known for their commercial TV ties, the emphasis in the new venture will be on 
taped software, cable and home video. ALEENE MacMINN 
</P>
</TEXT>
