PERSIAN GULF OIL RIG SINKS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
ABU DHABI, United Arab Emirates 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An offshore oil rig sank Wednesday in stormy gulf waters off Abu Dhabi, but no 
injuries were reported, shipping officials said. The officials said the rig was 
the JAKS 1, but they had no further details on its size or capacity. 
</P>
