courtroom to make their pleas. ; Photo, COLOR, Commissioner Richard Sullivan 
reflects in Orange County Harbor Municipal Court. ; Photo, COLOR, Defendant 
tells Sullivan mitigating circumstances that contributed to her citation. ; 
Photo, COLOR, Bail may be reduced significantly. ; Photo, Driver struggles to 
remain awake for his turn in traffic court. KEN HIVELY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
