witnessed the killing, originally identified the men for police in Greenville, 
and testified about the shooting before a grand jury in Chicago. Rosemond has 
testified that she was later attacked by gang member Freddie Sweeney, who said 
that he was hired by Robinson to kill Rosemond to keep her quiet. 
