<SUBJECT>
<P>
BROWN, DAVID A; BROWN, CINNAMON; CONSPIRACY; CONFESSIONS; MURDERS -- ORANGE 
COUNTY; AUDIO RECORDINGS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
